        "description": "Gradation 2 requires that validation experiments use the same pump geometry, fluid analogue, and operating range as the COU, with documented similarity analysis."
      },
      "rationale": "Validation experiments were performed on the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump geometry — the same geometry used in the COU simulations. Bovine blood analogue and operating envelope match the COU. Similarity analysis documented in Morrison et al. (2016). Gradation 2 achieved."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/factor/morrison-numerical-solver-error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
