      "rationale": "At MRL 2 for a Class II device, iterative convergence monitoring (residuals < 1e-5 for all equations, mass imbalance < 0.01%) is sufficient to bound solver error. A separate formal numerical solver error budget is scoped out; convergence criteria are documented in the simulation protocol and verified for all five operating points."
